Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,薰！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她看向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那时田雾姬好好看向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她对我说…「飞吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,田雾姬…
